<view class="page-wrapper">
  <!-- 顶部装饰 -->
  <view class="top-decoration">
    <view class="decoration-circle circle-1"></view>
    <view class="decoration-circle circle-2"></view>
    <view class="decoration-circle circle-3"></view>
  </view>

  <!-- 头部 -->
  <view class="header">
    <view class="logo-wrapper">
      <image class="logo" src="/images/Black_faced_spoonbill.jpeg" mode="aspectFill"></image>
    </view>
    <view class="title-group">
      <text class="title">深圳观鸟助手</text>
      <text class="subtitle">发现深圳丰富的鸟类多样性</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <!-- 功能卡片区 -->
  <view class="features">
    <view class="feature-card map" bindtap="goToMap">
      <view class="feature-left">
        <view class="feature-icon-bg">
          <text class="feature-icon">🗺️</text>
        </view>
        <view class="feature-info">
          <text class="feature-title">观鸟地图</text>
          <text class="feature-desc">查看深圳各区域鸟类分布</text>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="feature-arrow">›</view>
    </view>

    <view class="feature-card spots" bindtap="goToBirdingSpots">
      <view class="feature-left">
        <view class="feature-icon-bg">
          <text class="feature-icon">🔍</text>
        </view>
        <view class="feature-info">
          <text class="feature-title">推荐观鸟点</text>
          <text class="feature-desc">5大代表性观鸟地点</text>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="feature-arrow">›</view>
    </view>

    <view class="feature-card activity" bindtap="goToActivityCenter">
      <view class="feature-left">
        <view class="feature-icon-bg">
          <text class="feature-icon">🎯</text>
        </view>
        <view class="feature-info">
          <text class="feature-title">活动中心</text>
          <text class="feature-desc">识别挑战·知识问答·每日打卡</text>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="feature-arrow">›</view>
    </view>

    <view class="feature-card school" bindtap="goToSchool">
      <view class="feature-left">
        <view class="feature-icon-bg">
          <text class="feature-icon">📚</text>
        </view>
        <view class="feature-info">
          <text class="feature-title">观鸟学堂</text>
          <text class="feature-desc">学习与自然相处的正确价值观</text>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="feature-arrow">›</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <!-- 底部介绍 -->
  <view class="intro-card">
    <view class="intro-header">
      <text class="intro-icon">🦅</text>
      <text class="intro-title">关于深圳鸟类</text>
    </view>
    <text class="intro-text">
      深圳地处东亚-澳大利西亚候鸟迁飞通道，拥有丰富的鸟类多样性。深圳湾、红树林等湿地是重要的候鸟驿站，每年吸引数十万只候鸟在此停歇。
    </text>
    <view class="intro-stats">
      <view class="stat-item">
        <text class="stat-value">180+</text>
        <text class="stat-label">观测鸟种</text>
      </view>
      <view class="stat-divider"></view>
      <view class="stat-item">
        <text class="stat-value">5</text>
        <text class="stat-label">重点区域</text>
      </view>
      <view class="stat-divider"></view>
      <view class="stat-item">
        <text class="stat-value">50万+</text>
        <text class="stat-label">年停留候鸟</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>